        "emailType": "text",
        "message": "=Hi {{ $('Set FU2 Contact').first().json.contact_name }},\n\nI hope this message finds you well. This is my final follow-up regarding the {{ $json.job_title }} role at {{ $json.company_name }}.\n\nI remain genuinely excited about the opportunity to contribute to your team. If there's a better time to connect, or if the role has been filled, please don't hesitate to let me know.\n\nThank you for your time and consideration!\n\nBest regards,\nRahat Sayyed\n\nLinkedIn: {{ $('Set Global Vars').first().json.linkedinLink }}\nPortfolio: {{ $('Set Global Vars').first().json.portfolioLink }}",
